[
  {
    "startTime": 1.0,
    "endTime": 6.5,
    "text": "Black Friday, the official kick off to the holiday shopping season, and no other town does it quite as good as this one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.7,
    "endTime": 11.100000000000001,
    "text": "Now let's get out there and grab the best deal!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.2,
    "endTime": 13.5,
    "text": "We really need a new TV."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.6,
    "endTime": 17.93,
    "text": "Look, they have the new 75-inch Tegu ultra-smart LED TV for 75% off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.0,
    "endTime": 23.1,
    "text": "Oh, yeah, if you're one of the first ten shoppers in the store on Black Friday, and that's never gonna happen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.1,
    "endTime": 24.200000000000003,
    "text": "Well, why not?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.3,
    "endTime": 26.6,
    "text": "We have just as much of a shot as anybody else."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.7,
    "endTime": 29.3,
    "text": "I'm the number one shopper in America three years running."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.4,
    "endTime": 32.8,
    "text": "- I'm gonna buy all ten of those TVs, and I'm gonna sell them on ebay.  - That's not fair!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.9,
    "endTime": 34.9,
    "text": "Don't be a hero, Justin. Just give up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.3,
    "endTime": 42.199999999999996,
    "text": "Ever since I was a little boy, I knew I was good at one thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.3,
    "endTime": 44.3,
    "text": "Getting things on sale."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.4,
    "endTime": 48.8,
    "text": "Look, I know your dad died trying to get a discman for 65% off in '94..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.9,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "And wasn't it worth it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.1,
    "endTime": 50.7,
    "text": "Was it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.8,
    "endTime": 52.599999999999994,
    "text": "You are not your father!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.7,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "I think it's time for you to finally come out of the shadows!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.0,
    "endTime": 58.6,
    "text": "This is what I have to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.7,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "You're Oz Meredith!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.1,
    "endTime": 63.5,
    "text": "You got the Blu-ray player for 97% off back in 2012."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.6,
    "endTime": 65.5,
    "text": "That was a long time ago."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.6,
    "endTime": 67.19999999999999,
    "text": "I shop online now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.3,
    "endTime": 68.2,
    "text": "We need you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.3,
    "endTime": 69.5,
    "text": "I need you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.5,
    "endTime": 72.1,
    "text": "We start tomorrow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.2,
    "endTime": 77.10000000000001,
    "text": "You need to be in tip-top shape!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.2,
    "endTime": 79.10000000000001,
    "text": "Come on, you turkeys!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.2,
    "endTime": 80.8,
    "text": "This ain't Cyber Monday!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.4,
    "endTime": 85.5,
    "text": "This is the main show!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.6,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "You need to carry the box together!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.6,
    "endTime": 91.89999999999999,
    "text": "How bad do you want it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.8,
    "endTime": 95.0,
    "text": "Maybe you just ought to try Craigslist."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.1,
    "endTime": 96.5,
    "text": "Get me a light bulb."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.6,
    "endTime": 97.69999999999999,
    "text": "Now VHS."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.0,
    "endTime": 99.3,
    "text": "No! Again!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.4,
    "endTime": 100.60000000000001,
    "text": "Now you're cookin'!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.7,
    "endTime": 101.9,
    "text": "It's about finesse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 104.9,
    "text": "You trample the mannequin, you trample the shopper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 107.3,
    "text": "And we don't trample people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.4,
    "endTime": 109.0,
    "text": "You don't need to elbow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.1,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "Focus. Breathe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.1,
    "endTime": 113.0,
    "text": "And be great together!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.1,
    "endTime": 114.1,
    "text": "Zack, where are you going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.2,
    "endTime": 116.8,
    "text": "Mom wants to know if you're coming home for Thanksgiving dinner tomorrow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.9,
    "endTime": 118.60000000000001,
    "text": "I've got bigger plans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.7,
    "endTime": 119.7,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.2,
    "endTime": 122.7,
    "text": "Ryan, what happened to you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.8,
    "endTime": 123.89999999999999,
    "text": "Life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.2,
    "endTime": 125.5,
    "text": "Life happened to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.6,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "You were never built for the really big sales, Justin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.1,
    "endTime": 131.29999999999998,
    "text": "- All dreams and no fight.  - I miss you, Justin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.4,
    "endTime": 133.5,
    "text": "This is Black Friday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.6,
    "endTime": 136.9,
    "text": "When you were born, I promised your father that if anything ever happened to him..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.0,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "Do you get it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.1,
    "endTime": 139.2,
    "text": "... I'd take care of you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.4,
    "endTime": 144.70000000000002,
    "text": "- Oz!  - Oz?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.8,
    "endTime": 146.0,
    "text": "Oz, wake up, Oz."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.1,
    "endTime": 147.9,
    "text": "That's it. I'm done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.0,
    "endTime": 149.65,
    "text": "It's not over; Oz would have wanted us..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.7,
    "endTime": 151.0,
    "text": "Oz is dead!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.1,
    "endTime": 152.5,
    "text": "And I can't do this alone!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.1,
    "endTime": 155.2,
    "text": "You're not alone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.3,
    "endTime": 157.0,
    "text": "Come join me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.1,
    "endTime": 162.4,
    "text": "I would rather play Call of Duty on a 32-inch standard definition television with several broken pixels."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.7,
    "endTime": 179.29999999999998,
    "text": "You've had it in you all along, kid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.6,
    "endTime": 181.2,
    "text": "Your dad would be proud."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.3,
    "endTime": 184.60000000000002,
    "text": "This is about teamwork."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.7,
    "endTime": 187.2,
    "text": "This is about the man beside you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.3,
    "endTime": 191.8,
    "text": "You will never be better than when you are busting doors with your brother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.9,
    "endTime": 193.20000000000002,
    "text": "Remember that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.5,
    "endTime": 196.8,
    "text": "Find somebody you can trust."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.9,
    "endTime": 198.70000000000002,
    "text": "You can't put a price on that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.5,
    "endTime": 201.0,
    "text": "Can't discount that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.7,
    "endTime": 205.39999999999998,
    "text": "There's no coupon for friendship, son."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.1,
    "endTime": 207.7,
    "text": "That's not for sale."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.1,
    "endTime": 213.0,
    "text": "So, get in there and take what's yours!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.1,
    "endTime": 215.9,
    "text": "Greatness, friendship..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.4,
    "endTime": 219.6,
    "text": "And the 75-inch Tegu Ultra TV."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.2,
    "endTime": 224.7,
    "text": "♫ Witness what you got, and it's what it is. ♫"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.8,
    "endTime": 227.10000000000002,
    "text": "♫ This is how we ride, this is how we live. ♫"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.2,
    "endTime": 230.0,
    "text": "♫ Yeah, that's what it takes to be the best, man. ♫"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.1,
    "endTime": 231.6,
    "text": "It's here! It's here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.7,
    "endTime": 235.29999999999998,
    "text": "It's here..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.3,
    "endTime": 236.9,
    "text": "- What?  - Get it..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.0,
    "endTime": 238.5,
    "text": "There..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.6,
    "endTime": 241.29999999999998,
    "text": "- I think they got it. Get it!  - Yeah, you get it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.4,
    "endTime": 243.0,
    "text": "It's here."
  }
]